channel.title: Dead Hobbies Podcast
channel.description: It's hard to keep up with comics. Every Wednesday, join our resident experts John and Ally as they delve into the world of ink and paper. Hosted from Comics and Games in sunny Coconut Creek, Florida, the Dead Hobbies Podcast offers an inside look at the news and happenings in the comic world. Be sure to check us out on your favorite podcast app!
